%h2 Please login to the APNS Proxy
%p.intro
  Enter your username & password in order to login to this system.
  All login attempts are logged. Your IP address is #{request.ip}.


= form_tag do
  %dl
    %dt= label_tag :username
    %dd= text_field_tag :username, params[:username], :class => 'focus'
    %dt= label_tag :password
    %dd= password_field_tag :password
  %p.submit
    = submit_tag 'Login'
